query: SELECT vt.id, vt.fileId, vt.status, vt.transcriptionPhase, vt.transcriptionMethod, vt.confidence, vt.language, LEFT(vt.fullText, 200) as textPreview, LENGTH(vt.fullText) as textLength, JSON_LENGTH(vt.segments) as segmentCount, f.title FROM video_transcripts vt JOIN files f ON f.id = vt.fileId WHERE f.title LIKE '%Reel 3%' ORDER BY vt.id DESC LIMIT 5;
